metadata.description: Ryoshi Tales awaits all of our enthusiastic supporters. Get your hands on these exclusive Ryoshi Tales-themed VIP NFTs now! Coming with 8 different traits each with relevant attributes � body, background, tools, mouth, hair, miscellaneous, eyes, clothing � every NFT is completely unique. Discover the Legend of Izanami's Cradle.

Become the owner of unique lands, farm Resources, explore Points of Interest, fight Epic Bosses & receive Rare Artifacts and Weapons.

Level up the Buildings on your Land to Unlock Extra Staking Slots and Higher Bonuses. 
Are you ready? You can use $FRTN to acquire Land Deeds and become the first ever Ryoshi Dynasties official landowner.

The Mad Meerkat is inspired by the cheeky nature of the loveable rogues, who loves nothing more than cavorting together in the sun. An expansion from our OG Ethereum collection, these 10000 Next Gen Cro Meerkats will traverse the novel Cronos chain. Guided by the M.A.D values, we will embark on an adventure to explore and unlock all that lies within Cronos. With each Mad Meerkat sharing and learning from one another regardless the chain, it is our next step forward as one Burrow.

The Degen Mad Meerkat Collection is the symbol of True Madness within MM. Loving the thrill of celebrating highs and avenging lows, this is what it means to be on an Adventure like no other. MM has and will always be a movement for those who burn bright in the Madness no matter what happens. #MAD4LIFE.

The MM TreeHouse represents a celebration of inclusivity and empowerment amongst all. Connecting branches between all of Cronos, it is a shared space where innovation is created from discovering shared value between differences- To build a lush future for everyone to succeed in their unique ways. Welcome to Stage 2 of MM.

Time Cronos Planets are a collection from the Time Machine Eco, To provide our Resource mining for Time Wars Web3 game, Minting a Time Planet guarantees you weekly passive resources (before mint out) AND a boost in Time Adventures for resources gathered on adventures.
Various resources earned from playing Ryoshi Dynasties

Welcome to the D.G.Verse! Backed by Crypto.com Capital and Spartan Group, D.G.Pals is one of the first to redefine Web3 gaming with the first Interoperable NFT on the Cronos chain. The Special Edition Collection consists mainly of crossover characters from collaborations with other IPs. These NFTs will be able to participate in all of the games in the D.G.Verse. Do check out the D.G.Pals website for more information on the collection.

Collection of 8008 Boomers using crypto in the only way they know how. Everyone has felt like our Boomers at some point in their crypto journey but just like everyone else they will figure it out eventually. Founded by a fully doxed team of 11, Boomer Squad was established to build an ecosystem of on chain games, events, collections, and ecosystem developments that reflects value back to our Gen 0 Boomers through our Verified Distribution Contract called the "Mattress Fund" and Boomer DAO. Check out our GitBook for a full breakdown of everything already established and in the works in our ecosystem
5,000 Undead Space Apes on the Cronos Network. Royalties used for Community Prize Pools and Raffles.
Cronos Chimp Club is a collection of 10,000 uniquely generated Chimps on the Cronos Chain with various traits that celebrate the different aspects of the Cronos ecosystem.

Bored Candy NFTs are the official NFT collection of Bored Candy City, the newest Cronos Chain ecosystem comprised of $CANDY token, a DEX & AMM, Play 2 Earn Web3 Games and the first P2E Mobile Game listed in App Store & Play Store.
These NFTs can be staked in the DEX for a fixed amount of $CANDY per day OR for a share of 25% of ALL games revenues OR to boost farms APRs by up to 25%.
They will also bare utility in the web3 and mobile games in the future.

The glass champions of the MarbleVerse represent the core of creativity, design, and imagination. With their crafted simplicity, minimalistic posture and sturdy build, Marbles are created to battle through race tracks with the grace of a dancer and a strong will to win. Getting stronger as their flocks grow, Marble racers represent purity, open-mindedness, creativity, unbound potential, and unshakable love of our childhoods while reflecting the aesthetic of the contemporary world.
The Dooligans are designed to provide the DooNFT community with a limited sized collection that gives even more scarcity through classifications, making each Dooligan rare in itself.

Unlock the Madness within you. Find the equipment of choice that will best suit your style of battle. Different combinations produce a myriad of results, choose wisely.  All great battles evolve with time. Every season brings about new collections of Mad Sacks, offering different armament, weapons and rewards to upgrade the Madness.
Tata's Guardians: a 5000 piece AI generated art, that will be gamified, investment pool based, and the main NFT in the Tonic ecosystem.

D.G.P: New World Beta LIVE 23rd May & D.G.P: Legends Beta LIVE 31st May 2022!
Welcome to the D.G.Verse! Backed by Crypto.com Capital and Spartan Group, D.G.Pals is one of the first to redefine Web3 gaming with the first Interoperable NFT on the Cronos chain. The D.G.Pals Genesis Collection is the most privileged set of 10,000 NFT collection. Genesis NFT holders will be empowered with resources, airdrops and other perks to help the D.G.Pals Team build the D.G.Verse. You can check out how, by owning a Genesis D.G.Pal NFT, you can help expand Panterra, grow the player base and contribute to development on the D.G.Pals Whitepaper or website. AutoTicket is a collection of 2000+ utility-enabled PFP. With AutoTicket, you can unlock exclusive Auto Strategy Vaults from AutoSingle. Head over to https://autosingle.singlefinance.io/ for more information about AutoTicket.
A collection of 7007 Zoomers from the Boomer Squad Project. Built to play in the game branch of the Boomer Squad Ecosystem, Zoomers play while Boomers earn.

Argonauts is a collection of 8,888 unique utility-enabled characters that represents your unique identity on the Cronos chain. Each Argonaut holder gets access to utility across the Argo Protocol platform, exclusive treasure chest events, activated partnership experiences, future collections, and more.
The Flaming Phenix Club is a prestigious collection of 6,666 stunningly beautiful, fiery, and unique creatures apart of the Phenix Finance Ecosystem.

The Underworld is full of all kinds of creatures. During the CroSkulls adventures to the different regions of the Underworld, the CroSkulls often find regional eggs. Each season of CroSkulls explore new regions of the Underworld. Each season will have different seasonal pets. Once the eggs hatch, you will acquire a seasonal pet from that egg's region of the Underworld.

World of Cats is a handcrafted collection of 4444 Unique NFTs created by the artist Tam4tik with utility that is tied to the real world.
Each with their own identity to be discovered by its founder. 
In its purest form, WORLD OF CATS is the art of storytelling.
Curated By:  HiddenFishDAO�

Welcome to the D.G.Verse! Backed by Crypto.com Capital and Spartan Group, D.G.Pals is one of the first to redefine Web3 gaming with the first Interoperable NFT on the Cronos chain. The Limited Edition Collection contains some of the most unique D.G.Pals in the D.G.Verse. Limited Edition NFTs are extremely rare in circulation, with only 100-200 per release. Limited Edition D.G.Pal NFTs will be able to participate in all of the games in the D.G.Verse. Do check out the D.G.Pals website for more information on the collection.

The Pocket Demons project is a collection of 666 uniquely generated demon characters. Each Demon is generated from a pool of over 70 traits. These Demons also carry unique stats and attacks that are utilized in our P2E Game!

Boom Rooms - Brought to you by the Boomer Squad team is the main source of distribution for our ecosystem utility token $SCRATCH. Take your Boom Rooms and place room components in them to build up your room score which determines how much $SCRATCH you will be generating. These rooms are fully customized, build your own NFTs with Room Components and show off some flare with the Boom Room Cosmetic Components!

CRO CROW is the very first NFT deployed on the Cronos Chain.

Edition #1 was minted on block #946, just 1 hour and 27 minutes after Cronos was launched.

The CRO CROW Ecosystem revolves around this historic NFT and the art of Alemf, the artist behind the crows and some other side collections.

These NFTs can be staked to The Forest to passively earn $CRO which is automatically distributed from secondary market royalties and other sources of income.

CAW CAW!
Pixel art animated Wizards made by ShadowBright. Art and passion mixed in a magical potion. Part of the TENEBRA's DREAM brand.

Are you a serious griller? Do you want to control the flames of the grills? Then this is a DAO NFT you won't want to miss. From proposals to treasury spending La Brigade De Cuisine has it all. Brought to you by The Cronos Steakhouse.

CroSkull is a collection of 6.666 uniquely generated NFTs stored on the Cronos Chain. Each CroSkull NFT is based on 6+ attributes with different rarities. A CroSkull is not simply a PFP but is also the key to the insane Dr. Jiko's laboratory experiments.

This collection is themed around the Ryoshi Dynasties game by Ebisu's Bay. It will consist of 10,000 unique items, each focused on the concept of Kamiyo-nanayo, "Seven Generations of the Age of the Gods." This collection aims to offer a simple yet exciting experience, featuring elements like ranks and properties that will make them highly appealing for trading and minting. Primary intention behind introducing this collection is to maximize the benefits for the current holders of The Sports NFT, also known as the Beta Mascots ecosystem. The utility of this collection will be within the Ryoshi Dynasties game within Ebisu's Bay.

The CroDoo is an NFT project with a first generation of 5678 unique voodoo dolls PFP collectibles on Cronos blockchain. We aim for a long term project of which all holders of OG collection benefit from holding them.

Xmas is coming, and the Lotus Ocean Islands are covered in snow.  The characters of Ryoshi Tales have been preparing for the winter festivities!

From getting ready to weather the harsh climate to enjoying the frosted landscapes, the NFTs of the Ryoshi Xmas Tales NFT collection come jam-packed with seasonally appropriate traits that make each art piece completely unique. 

In addition, these NFTs will feature in the upcoming Ryoshi Tales game as they will provide special in-game bonuses.
So what are you waiting for? 

Get one now to sport your most Xmassy PFP to date.

Kaiju Madzilla are here! A randomly generated collection of 6,666 NFTs, they will serve as the core component of the Kaiju of Cronos Ecosystem. By harvesting Kaiju $ENRG, they will lead you on a journey to obtain true Kaiju $POWR. The era of the Kaiju are upon us...
